<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ - Books I’ve Read</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="faq.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>FAQ</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Find answers to common questions about my book collection and how I choose, read, and review books.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">What criteria do you use to select books?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">I select books based on a mix of personal interests, recommendations, and books that align with my ongoing learning goals. I enjoy exploring a variety of genres, including self-development, fiction, and science.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">How do you rate the books you read?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">I rate books based on how much value I get from them in terms of knowledge, entertainment, and emotional impact. I don’t follow a strict rating scale but focus on how well the book aligns with my personal objectives.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">How often do you update the book list?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">I update the book list regularly, usually once a month. The list is constantly evolving as I read more books, and I aim to add new entries as I finish them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">Where can I find these books?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">You can find these books on various platforms like Amazon, local bookstores, or libraries. I’ve also included ISBNs for many of the books, so you can easily find them in your local library or bookstore.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">Can I ask you for book recommendations?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">Yes! Feel free to reach out to me via email for book recommendations. I’d be happy to suggest books based on your interests or goals.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- New Question -->
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2 class="faq-question">Why did you start reading books?</h2>
            <p class="faq-answer">I started reading books because I wanted to improve my life and learn new things. Books provide valuable knowledge and insights that help me tackle challenges, expand my perspective, and grow both personally and professionally.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="faq-footer">
        <p>If you have any more questions, feel free to <a href="/contact">contact me</a>.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
